title: I Melted Every Halloween Candy Together
description:
HELLO FRIENDS!! Yes, we did something bad. Now, as you guys may know... I love halloween. From the spooky decorations to the costumes, to the candy, oh yes, THE CANDY. From Snickers to Skittles to every Reese's shape imaginable, I am a halloween candy fiend. 

So I had a horrible idea that I decided to act upon: what if we tried to melt every halloween candy together into a single franken-candy... the one candy to rule them all, and in the darkness, satiate my desire for an entire bucket of halloween candy in just one bite? 

Well, I guess we're gonna find out. Because that's what this video is about. 

Big thank you to Mat & StephPat from the Theorists, as well as Danielle & Karla from Escaz√π for being the guest tasters of our franken-candy bar!! You can find them here:
